Package uk.msci.project.rsa

Class ResultsView

java.lang.Object
uk.msci.project.rsa.ResultsView
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ResultsView extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The ResultsView class is responsible for displaying the statistical results of the benchmarking process in the digital signature application. It contains elements to visualise various statistics and buttons to export different types of data.

    • exportComparisonTableResultsToCSV

      public void exportComparisonTableResultsToCSV(String fileName)
      Exports the data from a comparison table to a CSV file. This method iterates through each item in the table and writes the data to a file with a CSV format. It also formats confidence interval values for better readability and replaces the column header "Conf. Interval" with "Confidence Interval".
      Parameters:
      fileName - The name of the file where the table data will be exported. This file will be created if it does not exist.

      public void updateGraphArea(org.jfree.chart.fx.ChartViewer chartViewer)

    • removeLastRow

      public void removeLastRow()
